But it has a plot. Two ex-lovers, now best friends, Beth and Susan, plan a reunion somewhere in the beautiful state of Oregon. Their current lovers, Chloe and Jesse, feel alienated as their girlfriends plan to attend several work-related seminars. Forced together, an intense attraction between Chloe and Jesse ignites a fiery affair, pitting stability, commitment and intimacy in their respective long-term relationships against the passion of new love (or is it just lust?). As feelings of guilt begin to surface, Chloe and Jesse deal with the ever increasing risk of getting caught.
